Title : Ronny Berg
Text : '''Ronny Berg''' (born 16 April 1970) is a [[Norway|Norwegian]] politician for the [[Progress Party (Norway)|Progress Party]].

He served as a deputy representative to the [[Parliament of Norway]] from [[Finnmark]] during the term [[2013 Norwegian parliamentary election|2013]]&ndash;2017. In total he met during 7 days of parliamentary session. From 2015 to 2017 he served in [[Solberg's Cabinet]] as a [[State Secretary (Norway)|State Secretary]] in the [[Ministry of Trade, Industry and Fisheries]].<ref>{{stortingetbio|ROB}}</ref> He was also the deputy mayor of [[Alta, Norway|Alta]].<ref>http://www.altaposten.no/lokalt/nyheter/article7021907.ece</ref>

